name: datalabeling
name_pretty: AI Platform Data Labeling Service V1beta1 API
ruby-cloud-description: AI Platform Data Labeling Service lets you work with human labelers to generate highly accurate labels for a collection of data that you can use in machine learning models. Note that google-cloud-data_labeling-v1beta1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-data_labeling instead. See the readme for more details.
